title: Westlife
date: 2013-06-02 11:41
comments: true
categories: 
---
Westlife is one of the best pop bands that ive ever heard. It disbanded in 2012 but it captivated the world with its melodious music since it released its first album in 1999. It comprised of the five memebers : Shane Filan, Mark Feehily, Brian Mcfadden, Nicky Byrne, Kian Egan but Brian Mcfadden left the band in 2003 due to his altercation with his band memebers. Westlife released its albums in consecutive years since 1999 except in 2008. Some of its singles like 'World Of Our Own', 'My Love', 'I Lay My Love on you' are still worldwide favourites today.
